                  </hi>. He never had authority to sell the samples at all.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> Very often a person will say, "I will take this pair, and bring me some more equal to them," and they have kept them—I had no doubt but Mr. Brandon would them have acknowledged that he had pout them into my beg—I have kept them one pair at time, and given then money—I was twelve years with Mr. Hook, in Board-street, and have lived in several respectable situation.</p>
